Introduction

Hwang Intak is a South Korean rapper, dancer, songwriter, and composer under FNC Entertainment. He is best known as one of the visuals of the boy group P1Harmony.

On September 16, Intak was revealed as the third member of P1Harmony. The group officially debuted on October 28, 2020, with their first mini-album "Disharmony : Stand Out".
